### Summary of Material Information (Substantial Holder Notice):  
- **Substantial Holder Change**: TAL Dai-ichi Life Australia Pty Ltd (TAL) acquired **33.2 million shares** (4.8% stake) in Challenger Limited (CGF) from AP Liberty GP, LLC for **A$247.6 million** on 16 June 2025.  
- **Total Voting Power Post-Acquisition**: TAL and associates (Dai-ichi Life Holdings, Inc. group) now hold **137.6 million CGF shares (19.9% stake)**, up from 104.4 million (15.1%).  

*Note: Excluded boilerplate legal details and associate entity listings (Annexures A/B).*
